-- Bayer to Move Accountancy Functions to East Europe, FTD Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-01-05T07:01:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-05/bayer-to-move-accountancy-functions-to-east-europe-ftd-reports.html
Bayer AG (BAYN)  plans to move some
accountancy operations from Leverkusen,  Germany , to a new
location in eastern  Europe ,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported
today, without saying where it obtained the information.  Bayer also plans to place its German patent departments in
a new subsidiary that will also be moved to a new location, the
newspaper said. Bayer has confirmed the information, FTD said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  